### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### OBSERVABILITY — Health checks, metrics, infrastructure
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── Gateway health ─────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/actuator/health

### ── Gateway routes ─────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/actuator/gateway/routes

### ── Prometheus metrics (via gateway) ───────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/actuator/prometheus

### ── Elasticsearch cluster health ───────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:19200/_cluster/health?pretty

### ── Elasticsearch product index stats ──────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:19200/products/_count?pretty

### ── Elasticsearch sample search ────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:19200/products/_search?pretty&q=telefon&size=3

### ── RabbitMQ overview (basic auth) ─────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:25672/api/overview
Authorization: Basic Z3Vlc3Q6Z3Vlc3Q=

### ── RabbitMQ queues ────────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:25672/api/queues
Authorization: Basic Z3Vlc3Q6Z3Vlc3Q=

### ── Redis ping ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### (Redis doesn't have HTTP — use redis-cli or check via product cache miss/hit)

### ── Eureka registered instances ────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:18761/eureka/apps
Accept: application/json

### ── Prometheus targets ─────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:19090/api/v1/targets

### ── Loki ready check ───────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:13100/ready

### ── Grafana health ─────────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:13001/api/health
